There are two things which sets apart a good thief from a poor
one.  One is the ability to swipe an item without getting caught.
The second one is stashing the item and getting out without being
detected.  Conceal is the ability of the skilled thief to obscure
an item from others view, usually by sneaking it into a cloak.

This is a guild level 7 ability. 

Syntax: conceal <item>

You can 'unhide' an item with that command. See 'thelp unhide'.
